flowchart TD
    SRC[Source Video] --> SPLIT[Split at GOPs<br/>ffmpeg -segment]
    SPLIT --> C1[Chunk 1]
    SPLIT --> C2[Chunk 2]
    SPLIT --> CN[Chunk N]
    C1 --> W1[Worker 1<br/>Encode]
    C2 --> W2[Worker 2<br/>Encode]
    CN --> WN[Worker N<br/>Encode]
    W1 --> CONCAT[Concatenate<br/>ffmpeg -concat]
    W2 --> CONCAT
    WN --> CONCAT
    CONCAT --> OUT[Final Output]
